snippet.textDisplay:
Oh my god!!! I have been listening to this ghazal by farida khanam ji since i was a toddler... I have a veryy old cassette which is still a very prized possession of mine.. And i havent been able to like any other rendition of this song by any singer ever.... And today watching farida khanum ji singing the most beautiful ghazal i have ever heard.... I got chills and i feel i have seen everythibg in life.... Even if i die now... It will be the most peaceful death i could ever imagine 😍😍😍💕💕💕😍😍😍
Ma'am lots and lots of love from india. Allah se bhagwaan se god se yahi dua hai ke ap aise hi gaati rahein humesha 💕
